title: The Real Housewives Of New York City S06E10 Bon Voyage Ramona WE
description: Heather attempts to calm the quarreling Kristen and Ramona with a dinner fit for a King. The next morning, the women are hiking in the woods when Ramona stumbles upon something that brings out her worst childhood horrors, causing her to flee the Berkshires. Then, the ladies enjoy a relaxing afternoon of sunbathing, swimming, and hitting on young men before a final dinner out where they devise a plan to give Ramona her "just desserts" for abandoning them under suspicious circumstances.
